%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20went%20to%20one%20of%20tech's%20most%20exclusive%20conferences%2C%20where%20Prince%20Harry%20and%20Kamala%20Harris%20mingled%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Upfront%20Summit%202025%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c1ea7169253ccddf97ea69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20closing%20party%20for%20Upfront%20Summit%202025%20at%20the%20Intuit%20Dome%20in%20Inglewood%2C%20CA.%3Cp%3EBen%20Bergman%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Upfront%20Summit%20is%20a%20glitzy%20annual%20invite-only%20conference%20hosted%20by%20Upfront%20Ventures.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%20expressed%20unease%20about%20the%20state%20of%20the%20tech%20market%2C%20which%20is%20dominated%20by%20AI%20mega-rounds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFormer%20Vice-President%20Kamala%20Harris%20held%20an%20hourlong%20private%20meeting%20at%20the%20conference%20focused%20on%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20do%20Prince%20Harry%2C%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20Bill%20Gurley%2C%20and%20Serena%20Williams%20have%20in%20common%3F%20Aside%20from%20all%20being%20famous%2C%20they%20were%20at%20this%20year's%20Upfront%20Summit%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fupfront-mark-suster-los-angeles-venture-capital-startup-tech-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglitzy%20annual%20invite-only%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20hosted%20by%20Upfront%20Ventures%20that%20aspires%20to%20be%20nothing%20like%20most%20of%20the%20stodgy%20events%20dotting%20the%20conference%20circuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20summit%20is%20held%20at%20a%20unique%20location%20yearly%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Rose%20Bowl%2C%20Malibu%20Farm%2C%20or%20the%20Academy%20Museum%20of%20Motion%20Pictures.%20This%20year's%20event%20was%20at%20the%20Intuit%20Dome%2C%20the%20new%20arena%20in%20Inglewood%2C%20CA%2C%20that%20is%20home%20to%20the%20NBA%20Clippers.%20There%20was%20pickup%20basketball%20at%20lunch%2C%20two%20illuminated%20hoops%20on%20the%20stage%2C%20and%20booming%20speaker%20introductions%20by%20the%20Clippers'%20public%20address%20announcer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20theme%20was%20ostensibly%20basketball%2C%20the%20more%20overriding%20one%20onstage%20and%20in%20conversations%20at%20couches%20and%20tables%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20area%20was%20the%20uneasy%20duality%20of%20the%20current%20tech%20market.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20venture%20investors%20are%20enamored%20of%20generative%20AI%2C%20which%20many%20see%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-investments-vcs-startups-valuations-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonce-in-a-generation%20moneymaking%20bonanza%3C%2Fa%3E%20bigger%20than%20the%20mobile%20phone.%20Megafunds%20like%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20and%20General%20Catalyst%20keep%20raising%20billions%20more%20to%20pile%20into%20the%20biggest%20AI%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20unique%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bill%20Gurley%2C%20general%20partner%20at%20Benchmark%20who%20backed%20startups%20like%20Uber%20and%20Zillow%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20stage.%20%26quot%3BAI%20is%20the%20exact%20event%20every%20founder%20and%20%5Bgeneral%20partner%5D%20dreams%20of.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20most%20VCs%20have%20been%20unable%20to%20return%20much%20capital%20to%20their%20limited%20partners%20because%20the%20IPO%20market%20has%20been%20slow%20to%20recover%2C%20and%20the%20M%26amp%3BA%20market%20has%20been%20quiet.%20Many%20startups%20have%20been%20going%20out%20of%20business%20as%20capital%20runs%20dry.%20There%20is%20also%20widespread%20concern%20those%20megafunds%20could%20be%20bad%20for%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20short-term%20pessimist%20and%20a%20long-term%20optimist%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pat%20Grady%2C%20partner%20at%20Sequoia%20Capital%2C%20in%20an%20on-stage%20interview.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20we're%20going%20to%20have%20a%20culling%20of%20the%20herd%20because%20people%20got%20away%20from%20the%20original%20spirit%20of%20venture%20capital%2C%20which%20is%20helping%20founders%20build%20legendary%20companies%2C%20and%20they%20got%20into%20the%20asset%20management%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeneral%20partners%20in%20a%20less%20enviable%20position%20than%20Grady%20pony%20up%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20to%20attend%20Upfront%2C%20and%20they%20are%20not%20paying%20for%20the%20food%20(which%20is%20always%20excellent)%20or%20the%20speakers%20(mostly%20top-caliber).%20Their%20return%20on%20investment%20is%20meeting%20the%20endowment%20heads%20and%20chief%20investment%20officers%20from%20places%20like%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan%20and%20Mizuho%2C%20who%20can%20write%20checks%20into%20their%20next%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20those%20LPs%20to%20make%20commitments%20proved%20frustratingly%20slow%20again%20this%20year%2C%20especially%20for%20less-established%20players%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20VCs%20and%20LPs%20I%20spoke%20to%20at%20the%20conference.%20Two%20LPs%20said%20they%20were%20impressed%20by%20the%20many%20funds%20they%20met%20with%2C%20but%20when%20I%20asked%20which%20funds%20they%20would%20invest%20in%2C%20they%20said%20they%20were%20not%20deploying%20any%20capital%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20gravity%20of%20tech%20has%20been%20moving%20rightward%20with%20Donald%20Trump's%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20the%20Upfront%20Summit%20retained%20its%20bluer%2C%20California%20vibe.%20There%20were%20appearances%20from%20Chelsea%20Clinton%20and%20Gov.%20Gavin%20Newsom%2C%20who%20received%20a%20frosty%20reception%20from%20some%20in%20the%20audience%20still%20upset%20about%20his%20handling%20of%20last%20month's%20catastrophic%20wildfires%20in%20LA.%20(Sequoia%20partner%20and%20Elon%20Musk%20confidant%20Shaun%20Macguire%2C%20as%20well%20as%20developer%20and%20former%20LA%2