2015%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20have%20enjoyed%20sunny%20days%20over%20the%20last%20two-and-a-half%20years%20thanks%20to%20a%20strong%20economy%20and%20enthusiasm%20around%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20some%20point%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20rain%2C%20warns%20Smead%20Capital%20Management%20founder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-bubble-unravel-interest-rates-sp500-outlook-smead-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBill%20Smead%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmead%20styles%20himself%20as%20a%20modern-day%20Noah%20of%20the%20financial%20world%2C%20drawing%20on%20the%20biblical%20tale%20of%20Noah's%20Ark.%20By%20that%20he%20means%20he's%20continuing%20to%20lean%20into%20value%20stocks%20as%20the%20growth%20factor%20remains%20frothy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20we%20have%20studied%20about%20common%20stocks%2C%20including%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Intelligent%20Investor%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20Ben%20Graham%2C%20%3Cem%3EA%20Short%20History%20of%20Financial%20Euphoria%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20John%20Kenneth%20Galbraith%2C%20and%20from%20listening%20to%20the%20wise%20words%20of%20Charlie%20Munger%20and%20Warren%20Buffett%20for%20decades%20leads%20us%20to%20believe%20that%20we%20must%20build%20a%20common%20stock%20portfolio%20which%20will%20float%20when%20the%20multi-year%20bear%20market%20creates%20a%20waterfall%20of%20selling%20among%20magnificent%20growth%20stocks%20and%20passive%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20Index%20owners%2C%26quot%3B%20Smead%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20letter%20to%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmead's%20downcast%20outlook%20stems%20in%20part%20from%20how%20fast%20this%20rally%20has%20unfolded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20most%20all-encompassing%20momentum%20market%20of%20my%2045%20years%20in%20the%20investing%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221664%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22s%26amp%3Bp%20500%20momentum%202014-2024%5C%22%2