rgh%2C%20but%20there%20are%20several%20Caledonian%20Sleeper%20routes%20throughout%20Scotland.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20map%20showing%20the%20main%20Caledonian%20Sleeper%20route%20to%20Edinburgh%2C%20and%20other%20routes%20to%20Glasgow%2C%20Fort%20William%2C%20Inverness%2C%20and%20Aberdeen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67af2b3b6630eb10385ca3d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Caledonian%20Sleeper's%20five%20routes.%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBI%3B%20Datawrapper%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglasgow-vs-edinburgh-scotland-family-vacation-destination-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlasgow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20train%20splits%20at%20the%20junction%20town%20of%20Carstairs%2C%20while%20all%20the%20other%20routes%20split%20at%20Edinburgh.%20(That%20includes%20the%20Fort%20William%20route%2C%20which%20then%20goes%20through%20a%20different%20station%20in%20Glasgow.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnless%20you've%20booked%20a%20seat%20instead%20of%20a%20room%2C%20you%20won't%20need%20to%20move%20during%20these%20splits%20%E2%80%94%20but%20you%20might%20wake%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20journey%20started%20at%20Euston%20%E2%80%94%20arguably%20the%20worst%20of%20London's%20train%20stations.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20concourse%20at%20London%20Euston%20station%20with%20several%20large%20departure%20boards%2C%20during%20a%20February%202025%20evening.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67af5cf66630eb10385ca997%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEuston%20was%20rebuilt%20in%20the%201960s.%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEuston%20has%2016%20platforms%20and%20is%20often%20very%20congested%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20was%20m