or%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20makers%20of%20this%20fifth-generation%20aircraft%20told%20BI%20their%20thoughts%20on%20how%20to%20address%20these.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELockheed%20Martin's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftest-pilot-shares-experience-flying-f-16-and-f-35-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EF-35%20Lightning%20II%20Joint%20Strike%20Fighter%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20combat-proven%20fifth-generation%20jet%2C%20but%20the%20supersonic%20stealth%20plane%20has%20consistently%20faced%20cost%20and%20readiness%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20recently%20visited%20the%20factory%20where%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-china-us-militaries-fifth-gen-fighter-jets-problems-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvanced%20aircraft%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20produced%20and%20asked%20the%20makers%20about%20the%20challenges%20facing%20this%20program%20and%20potential%20changes%20that%20might%20help%20reduce%20sustainability%20costs%20and%20improve%20mission%20capability%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lifetime%20F-35%20program%20costs%20are%20now%20expected%20to%20top%20%242%20trillion%2C%20and%20sustainability%20costs%20are%20rising.%20Yet%20the%20Government%20Accountability%20Office%20assessed%20last%20year%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-f-35-stealth-fighter-failed-mission-capable-goals-watchdog-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EF-35%20isn't%20hitting%20mission-capable%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20hasn't%20for%20years.%20These%20are%20key%20criticisms%20the%20fighter%20has%20faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Lockheed%20representative%20said%20that%20addressing%20these%20issues%20comes%20down%20to%20reliably%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ff35-fighters-mission-capable-just-over-half-the-time-watchdog-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvesting%20in%20parts%20and%20maintenance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Edward%20Smith%2C%20the%20company's%20F-35%20business%20development%20director%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bto%20maintain%20a%20fleet%20at%20any%20given%20readiness%20level%2C%20you%20have%20to%20fully%20fund%20your%20supply%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Joint%20Program%20Office%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-f-35-stealth-fighter-failed-mission-capable-goals-watchdog-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20readiness%20tends%20to%20improve%20with%20a%20healthy%20supply%20of%20parts%20for%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20said%20that%20the%20F-35%20has%20historically%20been%20underfunded%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20supply%20purchased%20for%20the%20aircraft%20and%20depot%20repair%20capacity%2C%20adding%20that%20it's%20important%20to%20get%20the%20supply%20of%20sustainment%20parts%20at%20a%20level%20that%20matches%20the%20jet's%20readiness%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223525%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20F-35%20performs%20a%20demonstration%20flight%20at%20the%20International%20Paris%20Air%20Show%20in%20June%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c21fd5b1834fe31165d85d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20F-35%20performs%20a%20demonstration%20flight%20at%20the%20International%20Paris%20Air%20Show%20in%20June%202023.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FMichel%20Euler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20parts%20are%20available%20and%20on%20the%20shelf%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20then%20%26quot%3Bwe%20can%20get%20to%20the%20readiness%20rates%20that%20are%20desired%20by%20all%20of%20our%20customers%20that%20are%20out%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20overall%20costs%2C%20he%20said%20that%20as%20more%20F-35s%20roll%20off%20the%20production%20line%20and%20the%20supply%20pool%20of%20parts%20grows%2C%20the%20aircraft%20will%20become%20increasingly%20cheaper%20to%20operate.%20Over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20explained%20Smith%2C%20it%20has%20seen%20a%2050%25%20reduction%20in%20cost-per-flight-hour%2C%20in%20some%20cases%20making%20it%20as%20expensive%20to%20fly%20as%20fourth-generation%20jets%20being%20made%20today%20but%20delivering%20more%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20said%20that%20the%20average%20mission%20capability%20rates%20for%20the%20F-35%2C%20which%20is%20the%20percentage%20of%20time%20it%20can%20perform%20one%20mission%2C%20tend%20to%20be%20between%20the%20high%2050s%20and%20high%2060s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20figures%20are%20higher%20on%20combat%20deployments%3B%20the%20US%20military%20averages%20an%2080%25%20mission%20capability%20rate%20for%20the%20F-35%20on%20every%20combat%20deployment%20it's%20done%2C%20and%20for%20the%20Israelis%2C%20since%20the%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20Hamas%20attacks%2C%20the%20number%20is%20almost%2090%25%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20exactly%20matches%20our%20funding%20level%20for%20parts.%20Traditionally%2C%20we've%20been%20funded%20at%20about%2070%25%20availability%2C%20and%20that's%20if%20nothing%20broke%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20fund%20supply%2C%20you%20cannot%20have%20the%20readiness%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227e423298-afc5-4671-8e59-9e6f79d63398%5C%22%3EA%20combat-proven%20fifth-gen%20fighter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F-35%20is%20the%20US%20military's%20second%20fifth-generation%20fighter%20jet%20after%20the%20air-superiority%20F-22%20Raptor.%20The%20jet%20comes%20in%20three%20variants%20designed%20for%20conventional%20runway%20and%20ship-based%20operations%20and%20is%20flown%20by%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%20Marine%20Corps%2C%20and%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224722%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20F-35%20idles%20on%20the%20flight%20deck%20of%20the%20amphibious%20assault%20ship%20USS%20Tripoli%20during%20night%20flight%20operations%20in%20January%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c220c569253ccddf97f63e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223145%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20F-35%20idles%20on%20the%20flight%20deck%20of%20the%20amphibious%20assault%20ship%20USS%20Tripoli%20during%20night%20flight%20operations%20in%20January%202022.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%201st%20Class%20Peter%20Burghart%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20military%20has%20flown%20all%20three%20F-35%20variants%20%E2%80%94%20the%20A%2C%20B%2C%20and%20C%20variants%20%E2%80%94%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-strikes-iran-shows-f-35-ready-higher-level-war-2024-12%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIsraeli%2520F%252D35s%2520have%2520previously%2Cthe%2520Taliban%252C%2520and%2520the%2520Houthis.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrike%20missions%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20terror%20groups%20in%20Iraq%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20and%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20were%20the%20first%20to%20fly%20the%20jet%20into%20battle.%20They%20operate%20their%20own%20version%20(the%20F-35I)%20and%20have%20flown%20it%20into%20combat%2C%20battling%20Syrian%20missile%20batteries%2C%20shooting%20down%20drones%2C%20and%20striking%20Iranian%20military%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jets%2C%20however%2C%20were%20built%20for%20a%20higher%20level%20of%20warfare%2C%20which%20would%20demand%20the%20advantages%20offered%20by%20its%20all-aspect%20stealth%2C%20sensor%20suite%2C%20networked%20systems%2C%20and%20combat%20power%2C%20all%20capabilities%20required%20for%20combating%20next-gen%20aircraft%20and%20high-end%20surface-to-air%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F-35%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-mile-long-factory-where-f-35-stealth-fighters-made-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeveloped%20and%20manufactured%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20part%20of%20a%20multinational%20partnership%2C%20and%20over%201%2C110%20jets%20have%20been%20delivered.%20Many%20US%20allies%20operate%20the%20aircraft%2C%20with%20more%20countries%20looking%20to%20acquire%20this%20plane%20in%20the%20future.%20It's%20considered%20a%20cornerstone%20for%20US%20airpower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22948449b4-e449-443f-89cc-586063043b0a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EImproving%20the%20program%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F-35%20program%20relies%20on%20a%20shared%20contractor%20and%20government-based%20maintenance%20system.%20How%20contracts%20are%20issued%20may%20affect%20how%20readiness%20issues%20are%20fixed.%20To%20increase%20efficiency%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20need%20to%20drive%20to%20more%20performance-based%20sustainment%20contracts%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227881%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Dutch%20F-35%20fighter%20jet%20is%20pictured%20at%20an%20Estonian%20airbase%20in%20February%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c21f5169253ccddf97f5f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225257%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Dutch%20F-35%20fighter%20jet%20is%20pictured%20at%20an%20Estonian%20airbase%20in%20February%202025.%3Cp%3EPatrick%20van%20Katwijk%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20sustainment%20for%20the%20F-35%20is%20contracted%20on%20an%20annual%20basis.%20He%20called%20this%20process%20inefficient%20and%20%26quot%3Bvery%20costly%2C%26quot%3B%20arguing%20that%20it%20doesn't%20allow%20the%20industry%20to%20plan%20and%20invest%20strategically%20because%20it's%20uncertain%20what%20the%20next%20annual%20contract%20could%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20definitely%20room%20to%20increase%20efficiency%20in%20how%20we%20contract%20for%20these%20systems%20and%20put%20the%20onus%20on%20industry%20to%20perform%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20we%20continue%20to%20strive%20for%20is%20those%20performance-based%20contracts%20that%20we%20not%20only%20get%20as%20a%20prime%2C%20but%20also%20with%20our%20suppliers%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said%2C%20noting%20this%20gives%20them%20%26quot%3Blong-term%20certainty%20and%20forecasting%20so%20we%20can%20invest%20to%20improve%20the%20metrics%20for%20this%20airplane.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerformance-based%20contracting%20is%20centered%20on%20the%20results%20achieved%20from%20a%20specific%20program%20in%20terms%20of%20requirements%20rather%20than%20the%20cost%20or%20time%20needed%20to%20ultimately%20achieve%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Bohnert%2C%20a%20licensed%20engineer%20at%20the%20RAND%20Corporation%2C%20said%20that%20longer-term%20contracts%20tend%20to%20be%20more%20efficient%20than%20annual%20contracts%20for%20long-term%20acquisition%20because%20they%20provide%20the%20industry%20an%20opportunity%20to%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerformance-based%20contracts%20%26quot%3Bcan%20be%20an%20effective%20tool%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20they%20require%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20the%20systems%20to%20set%20adequate%20performance%20goals%20with%20accurate%20pricing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224423%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Israeli%20F-35%20flies%20during%20a%20graduation%20ceremony%20for%20new%20pilots%20at%20the%20Hatzerim%20airbase%20near%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20Beersheba%20in%20June%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c2211569253ccddf97f652%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222949%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Israeli%20F-35%20flies%20during%20a%20graduation%20ceremony%20for%20new%20pilots%20at%20the%20Hatzerim%20airbase%20near%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20Beersheba%20in%20June%202023.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FTsafrir%20Abayov%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F-35%20JPO%2C%20which%20leads%20the%20aircraft's%20life-cycle%20program%20management%2C%20acknowledged%20that%20annualized%20sustainment%20contracts%20are%20not%20ideal%20for%20reducing%20costs%20and%20improving%20readiness.%20However%2C%20it%20said%20bad%20performance%20contracts%20can%20arguably%20be%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKey%20considerations%20for%20performance%20contracts%20include%20funding%20stability%20for%20sustainment%2C%20confidence%20in%20data%20for%20forecasting%20and%20cost%20modeling%2C%20and%20contract%20structures%20that%20balance%20risk%20between%20industry%20and%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20JPO%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerformance%20contracts%20must%20align%20with%20warfighter%20needs%2C%20potentially%20requiring%20a%20mix%20of%20contracting%20strategies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Lockheed%20Martin%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20company%20is%20committed%20to%20working%20with%20the%20JPO%20%26quot%3Bon%20delivering%20mission-essential%20and%20effective%20sustainment%20support%20for%20the%20F-35%20program%20now%20and%20in%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20said%20pursuing%20a%20performance-based%20contracting%20strategy%20is%20a%20decision%20made%20by%20the%20Pentagon.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20defer%20you%20to%20them%20for%20further%20comment.%20We%20support%20any%20model%20that%20can%20increase%20readiness%20and%20reduce%20cost%20for%20our%20customer%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-f-35-jet-makers-need-tackle-cost-readiness-concerns-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740821402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c2213669253ccddf97f659%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-f-35-jet-makers-need-tackle-cost-readiness-concerns-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20supersonic%20aircraft%20is%20widely%20recognized%20as%20a%20top%20fifth-generation%20fighter%20jet%2C%20but%20the%20program%20has%20faced%20criticisms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jepstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Jake%20Epstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-f-35-jet-makers-need-tackle-cost-readiness-concerns-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20dreaded%20S-word%3A%20Stagflation%20concerns%20are%20creeping%20back%20into%20the%20US%20economic%20picture%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20illustation%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20Building%20with%20a%20red%20downward%20arrow%20above%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b0fb95393cd3c8629b50a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EiStock%3B%20Rebecca%20Zisser%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETop%20economists%20are%20eyeing%20the%20rising%20risk%20that%20the%20US%20will%20be%20hit%20with%20a%20bout%20of%20stagflation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20a%20painful%20scenario%20that%20entails%20higher%20inflation%20and%20slower%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKansas%20City%20Fed%20president%20Jeff%20Schmid%20this%20week%20highlighted%20the%20risk%20of%20that%20combined%20scenario.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFears%20of%20a%20dire%20economic%20scenario%20have%20crept%20into%20the%20discussion%20recently%2C%20with%20top%20commentators%20this%20week%20expressing%20concern%20the%20US%20could%20be%20headed%20for%20a%20period%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-stagflation-explained-oil-outlook-low-growth-high-inflation-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estagflation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20scenario%20entails%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-higher-inflation-fed-interest-rates-taxes-mortgage-rates-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20inflation%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-job-cuts-government-spending-stock-market-immigration-economic-growth-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%20economic%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20two%20things%20that%20don't%20normally%20go%20hand%20in%20hand.%20Stagflation%20slammed%20the%20US%20during%20the%201970s%20and%20economists%20say%20it%20can%20be%20even%20trickier%20for%20policymakers%20to%20resolve%20than%20a%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20central%20bankers%20would%20typically%20cut%20interest%20rates%20in%20response%20to%20slowing%20economic%20growth%2C%20high%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-inflation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einflation%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20make%20the%20Fed%20hesitant%20to%20loosen%20financial%20conditions%20any%20further%2C%20leaving%20their%20hands%20tied%20in%20both%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeff%20Schmid%2C%20the%20Kansas%20City%20Fed%20president%2C%20has%20suggested%20such%20a%20scenario%20is%20already%20on%20his%20radar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20risks%20to%20inflation%20appear%20to%20be%20to%20on%20the%20upside%2C%20discussions%20with%20contacts%20in%20my%20district%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20recent%20data%2C%20suggest%20that%20elevated%20uncertainty%20might%20weigh%20on%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmid%20said%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Virginia%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20presents%20the%20possibility%20that%20the%20Fed%20could%20have%20to%20balance%20inflation%20risks%20against%20growth%20concerns.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20that%20same%20day%2C%20Torsten%20Sl%C3%B8k%20%E2%80%94%20the%20chief%20economist%20of%20Apollo%20Global%20Management%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2F2025-02-27%2Fapollo-s-slok-on-doge-job-cuts-and-stagflation-concerns-video%3Fsref%3DLspf