py%20with%20his%20work%20so%20far%20%E2%80%94%20except%20for%20his%20actions%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-withdraws-student-loan-forgiveness-plan-debt-relief-trump-education-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudent%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20disappointing%20that%20it%20feels%20like%20we're%20just%20getting%20left%20behind%2C%26quot%3B%20Stephens%2C%2035%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20like%20they're%20just%20going%20to%20leave%20everybody%20to%20either%20pay%20it%20or%20suffer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephens%20is%20enrolled%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstudent-loans%2Fhow-to-apply-for-income-driven-repayment-student-loans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESAVE%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-permanently-struck-down-student-loan-borrowers-lose-relief-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20federal%20court%20recently%20paused%3C%2Fa%3E%20pending%20a%20final%20court%20decision.%20It%20was%20established%20by%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20in%202023%20and%20intended%20to%20give%20student-loan%20borrowers%20cheaper%20monthly%20payments%20with%20a%20shorter%20timeline%20for%20loan%20forgiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20Stephens%20owed%20%240%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emonthly%20based%20on%20her%20income%20level.%20If%20SAVE%20goes%20away%2C%20she%20said%20she%20cannot%20afford%20higher%20payments%20while%20also%20financially%20supporting%20her%20two%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20didn't%20have%20our%20family%20support%20helping%20us%20with%20the%20kids%20and%20food%20and%20stuff%20like%20that%2C%20we%20would%20not%20be%20making%20it%20every%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20Stephens%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe'd%20be%20losing%20our%20house%20and%20everything%2C%20so%20we%20can't%20even%20imagine%20to%20start%20paying%20on%20those%20loans%20yet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20heard%20from%20dozens%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%20over%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%20who%20said%20they're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-broad-student-loan-forgiveness-is-over-borrowers-uncertainty-trump-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworried%20about%20the%20SAVE%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20eliminated%20and%20are%20concerned%20with%20facing%20potentially%20higher%20monthly%20payments.%20While%20the%20legal%20fate%20of%20the%20plan%20is%20still%20in%20limbo%2C%20borrowers%20are%20stuck%20wondering%20when%20they'll%20have%20to%20resume%20repayment%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20much%20the%20bill%20will%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20legal%20challenges%20seeking%20to%20block%20the%20plan%2C%20January%20guidance%20from%20the%20Education%20Department%20said%20that%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20SAVE%20will%20make%20payments%20%26quot%3Bno%20earlier%26quot%3B%20than%20December.%20Interest%20is%20not%20accruing%20on%20their%20balances%20during%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20recent%20court%20decision%20keeping%20SAVE%20paused%2C%20acting%20undersecretary%20of%20education%2C%20James%20Bergeron%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20ruling%20%26quot%3Bis%20good%20news%20for%20hardworking%20American%20taxpayers%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Department%20of%20Education%20is%20currently%20working%20to%20ensure%20borrowers%20understand%20existing%20repayment%20alternatives%20allowed%20under%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Bergeron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephens%20said%20she%20doesn't%20see%20it%20that%20way%20%E2%80%94%20and%20hopes%20the%20Trump%20administration%20prioritizes%20relief%20for%20student-loan%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20it%20helped%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20it's%20really%20heartbreaking%20that%20it%20just%20ended%20with%20nothing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204b24fe6-6814-43fa-bd50-6c0d65d750f5%5C%22%3E'It's%20going%20to%20be%20very%20scary'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMike%20Rendino%2C%2051%2C%20accrued%20student%20debt%20in%20his%2030s%20when%20he%20went%20back%20to%20school%20to%20advance%20his%20career.%20When%20his%20job%20relocated%20and%20he%20couldn't%20move%2C%20he%20found%20himself%20out%20of%20work%20and%20deferred%20his%20loans.%20But%20interest%20continued%20to%20accumulate%20during%20those%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnrolling%20in%20SAVE%20allowed%20Rendino%20to%20pay%20%24160%20each%20month%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20felt%20was%20affordable.%20Now%2C%20however%2C%20he%20no%20longer%20feels%20confident%20with%20his%20payoff%20plan%2C%20which%20he%20said%20is%20projected%20to%20be%20just%20under%20%241%2C000%20a%20month%20without%20SAVE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20very%20scary%20to%20figure%20this%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Rendino%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20program%20is%20literally%20allowing%20me%20to%20fulfill%20my%20financial%20obligations%20back%20to%20the%20government%20for%20those%20federal%20loans%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bit's%20not%20that%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20repay%20it%2C%20it's%20that%20I%20just%20cannot%20afford%20to%20pay%20the%20kind%20of%20money%20that%20they%20want.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrigitte%20Knudson%2C%2056%2C%20is%20also%20struggling%20with%20SAVE's%20uncertain%20fate.%20While%20Knudson%20said%20she's%20still%20been%20making%20payments%20during%20this%20time%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%200%25%20interest%20rate%2C%20she's%20prepared%20to%20push%20off%20her%20retirement%20to%20afford%20potentially%20higher%20monthly%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20extra%20dollar%20that%20I%20get%20is%20going%20to%20pay%20down%20this%20loan%20because%20I%20know%20there's%20going%20to%20