wift%20response%20teams%2C%20comprising%20more%20than%20100%20personnel%20from%20the%20Ibex%20Brigade%2C%20specially%20trained%20for%20high-altitude%20rescue%20operations%2C%20were%20immediately%20mobilised.%20The%20teams%20included%20doctors%20and%20ambulances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDRF%20said%20it%20rushed%20four%20teams%20to%20Chamoli.%20Besides%2C%20another%20four%20units%20have%20been%20kept%20on%20standby%2C%20NDRF%20Director%20General%20(DG)%20Piyush%20Anand%20told%20PTI.%20Officials%20said%20two%20teams%20were%20rushed%20from%20the%20Regional%20Response%20Centre%20(RRC)%20of%20the%20NDRF%20in%20Dehradun%2C%20while%20the%20other%20two%20were%20diverted%20from%20Joshimath%2C%20about%2050%20km%20from%20Mana%2C%20where%20they%20were%20undertaking%20a%20familiarisation%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force's%20(IAF)%20Mi-17%20choppers%20left%20for%20Mana%20on%20Saturday%20morning%20to%20join%20the%20search-and-rescue%20operations.%20The%20Mana%20helipad%20was%20opened%2C%20where%2014%20civilians%20were%20rescued%2C%20one%20of%20them%20in%20critical%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUttarakhand%3A%20The%20Mana%20avalanche%20rescue%20operation%20has%20started%20with%20helicopter%20rescues%20from%20Joshimath%20base%20camp.%20Two%20helicopters%20were%20sent%20to%20Badrinath%20Dham%2C%20with%20one%20returning%20from%20Mana%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbtS9IkR8Hd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbtS9IkR8Hd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20IANS%20(%40ians_india)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fians_india%2Fstatus%2F1895678510527840659%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%201%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttarakhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20is%20continuously%20reviewing%20the%20ongoing%20rescue%20operations%20from%20the%20CM's%20resi