e%20was%20meticulously%20categorised%20and%20sent%20to%20the%20appropriate%20recycling%20centres%20and%20composting%20facilities%2C%20ensuring%20that%20absolutely%20nothing%20from%20the%20wedding%20ended%20up%20in%20a%20landfill.%20By%20embracing%20zero-waste%20principles%20such%20as%20mindful%20material%20sourcing%2C%20reusable%20decor%2C%20and%20responsible%20waste%20management%2C%20couples%20can%20drastically%20reduce%20their%20environmental%20footprint.%20More%20importantly%2C%20integrating%20conversations%20around%20sustainability%20into%20the%20celebration%20can%20encourage%20guests%20to%20adopt%20low-waste%20habits%20in%20their%20everyday%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20waste-conscious%20mindset%20even%20extended%20to%20the%20wedding%20favours.%20Instead%20of%20the%20usual%20trinkets%2C%20the%20couple%20chose%20to%20give%20guests%20organic%20honey%20from%20a%20local%20Goan%20apiary%2C%20packaged%20in%20glass%20jars%2C%20sourced%20by%20them.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20honour%20our%20guests%20with%20something%20sustainable%2C%20and%20organic%20honey%20seemed%20like%20the%20perfect%20gift%2C%E2%80%9D%20Svetlana%20shares.%20For%20their%20bridesmaids%20and%20best%20men%2C%20they%20curated%20zero-waste%20gift%20boxes%20containing%20organic%20products%20like%20deodorants%2C%20lip%20balms%2C%20soaps%2C%20and%20moisturisers%2C%20handcrafted%20by%20local%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20transportation%2C%20the%20couple%20took%20steps%20to%20reduce%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20by%20arranging%20shuttle%20buses%20for%20guests.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20minimise%20the%20number%20of%20cars%20at%20the%20wedding%20to%20reduce%20pollution%2C%20so%20we%20organised%20three%20shuttle%20buses%2C%E2%80%9D%20Svetlana%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20asked%20guests%20not%20to%20bring%20physical%20gifts%20but%20instead%20contribute%20to%20a%20social%20impact%20registry%2C%20where%20they%20could%20donate%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%