m%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fdragon-box-office-collection-day-8-pradeep-ranganathans-entertainer-enters-week-3-with-a-steady-business%2Farticleshow%2F118641423.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Donald%20Trump%20Says%20US%20Plans%20Return%20To%20Afghanistan%20%26quot%3BBecause%20Of%20China%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20has%20made%20a%20new%20announcement%20with%20regard%20to%20Afghanistan%20-%20that%20the%20US%20is%20planning%20to%20go%20back.%20%26quot%3BJoe%20Biden%20gave%20it%20up...I%20think%20we%20should%20get%20it%20back%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%2C%20talking%20about%20armoured%20vehicles%20and%20the%20strategic%20Bagram%20Airbase.%20President%20Trump's%20remarks%20came%20at%20a%20press%20briefing%20after%20his%20first%20Cabinet%20meeting%20since%20he%20took%20over%20commander-and-chief%20of%20the%20US%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20more%20specific%20about%20what%20he%20meant%2C%20President%20Trump%20said%20%26quot%3BWhat%20has%20bothered%20me%20very%20much%20is%20that%20we%20gave%20billions%20and%20billions%20of%20dollars%20to%20Afghanistan%2C%20nobody%20knows%20that%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20we%20left%20behind%20all%20of%20that%20equipment%2C%20which%20would%20not%20have%20happened%20had%20I%20been%20president%20at%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20(US)%20were%20getting%20out%20under%20my%20presidency.%20I%20am%20the%20one%20who%20got%20our%20military%20presence%20to%20under%205%2C000%2C%20but%20we%20were%20going%20to%20keep%20Bagram%20(air%20base)%20-%20not%20because%20of%20Afghanistan%2C%20but%20because%20of%20China%2C%20because%20the%20air%20base%20is%20exactly%20one%20hour%20from%20where%20China%20makes%20its%20nuclear%20missiles.%20So%2C%20we%20were%20going%20to%20keep%20Bagram%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20%26quot%3BBagraom%20airbase%20is%20the%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20airbases%20in%20the%20world.%20It%20has%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20and%20most%20powerful%20runways.%20Very%20heavy%20concrete%20and%20steel%20was%20used%20(to%20strengthen)%20it.%20Anything%20could%20be%20carried%20on%20it.%20And%20we%20gave%20it%20up%20-%20and%20you%20know%20who%20is%20occupying%20it%20at%20the%20moment%3F%20China.%20Because%20Biden%20gave%20it%20up.%20So%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20keep%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20US%20only%20looks%20to%20keep%20a%20small%20troops%20presence%20in%20Afghanistan%20(especially%20Bagram)%2C%20President%20Trump%20further%20noted%20that%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20is%20now%20going%20to%20keep%20that%20(Bagram)%26quot%3B.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20US%20military%20will%20perform%20a%20%26quot%3Bwithdrawal%20of%20all%20the%20equipment%20left%20behind%20-%20about%2040%2C000%20armoured%20and%20military%20heavy%20vehicles%26quot%3B%20currently%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Taliban%20government%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20calling%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20US%20withdrew%20from%20Afghanistan%20%26quot%3Bdisgraceful%26quot%3B%2C%20President%20Trump%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3BIn%20all%20fairness%20to%20Putin%20-%20When%20he%20saw%20that%2C%20he%20decided%20'Well%2C%20this%20is%20our%20time%20to%20go%20into%20Ukraine%2C%20because%20the%20timing%20seemed%20just%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaying%20that%20Afghanistan%20is%20being%20able%20to%20stay%20afloat%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Bbillions%20of%20dollars%20of%20aid%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20US%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bnobody%20talked%20about%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20that%2C%20with%20him%20as%20President%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20America%20seems%20to%20know%20about%20now%26quot%3B%2C%20President%20Trump%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bsince%20we%20are%20sending%20aid%2C%20they%20(Afghan%20government)%20should%20give%20it%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202021%2C%20amid%20deepening%20crisis%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20then%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20had%20defended%20his%20move%20for%20a%20complete%20withdrawal%20of%20troops%20from%20the%20war-torn%20country%2C%20saying%20that%20history%20will%20record%20this%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Blogical%2C%20rational%2C%20and%20right%20decision%26quot%3B.%20Joe%20Biden's%20decision%20had%20come%20twenty%20years%20after%20the%20US%20invasion%20of%20Afghanistan%20following%20the%209%2F11%20terror%20attack%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConservative%20estimates%20suggest%20that%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20lives%20were%20lost%20in%20the%20twenty-year%20war%20in%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20official%20response%2C%20either%20from%20the%20Afghan%20Taliban%20or%20from%20China%2C%20which%20President%20Trump%20accused%20of%20having%20a%20military%20presence%20in%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bagram%20airbase%20was%20originally%20constructed%20by%20USSR%20during%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20after%20the%20Soviet%20invasion%20of%20Afghanistan%2C%20when%20US%20too%20tried%20to%20grow%20its%20influence%20in%20Afghanistan.%20Many%20years%20after%20the%20Soviet%20withdrawal%2C%20and%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20the%20US%20returned%20to%20Afghanistan%20to%20wage%20a%20war%20on%20Osama%20bin%20Laden.%20It%20was%20then%20that%20the%20US%20took%20over%20Bagram%20airbase%20and%20strengthened%20it.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740802020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fef85092o_donald-trump-reuters_625x300_27_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-says-us-plans-return-to-afghanistan-because-of-china-watch-7819681%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20has%20made%20a%20new%20announcement%20with%20regard%20to%20Afghanistan%20-%20that%20the%20US%20is%20planning%20to%20go%20back.%20%26quot%3BJoe%20Biden%20gave%20it%20up...I%20t