%20More%20on%20that%20in%20the%20camera%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOtherwise%2C%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20features%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-action-button-replacing-ring-silent-switch-since-first-iphone-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAction%20button%3C%2Fa%3E%20introduced%20with%20the%20iPhone%2015%20Pro%20models.%20It%20performs%20the%20same%20functions%20and%20shortcuts%20as%20other%20iPhones%20with%20the%20Action%20button%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20useful%20and%20appreciated%20addition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20won't%20find%20the%20Camera%20Control%20button%20introduced%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fiphone-16%23new-buttons%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiPhone%2016%20series%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20iPhone%2016e%2C%20and%20I'm%20fine%20with%20that%20%E2%80%94%20it%20hasn't%20proven%20indispensable%20to%20the%20iPhone%20experience%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ed23f86-aa21-49c4-9c0f-89243d112dfd%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Performance%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerformance%3A%20Flagship%20power%20for%20a%20mid-range%20price%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20things%20about%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20is%20its%20astounding%20performance%20and%20its%20potential%20longevity%20for%20the%20price.%20It%20runs%20on%20Apple's%20latest%20A18%20processor%20with%20four%20GPU%20cores%2C%20which%20is%20one%20fewer%20than%20the%20iPhone%2016's%20version%20of%20the%20processor%20with%20five%20GPU%20cores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20opens%20and%20runs%20apps%20as%20quickly%20as%20we%20expect%20a%20new%20phone%20running%20on%20the%20latest%20processor%20available.%20Benchmark%20results%20are%20aligned%20with%20the%20iPhone%2016's%20A18%20processor%20for%20single-core%20performance%20(running%20active%20apps).%20Multicore%20benchmark%20scores%20(background%20apps%20and%20processes)%20are%20slightly%20lower%20but%20almost%20wit