Apple%20Intelligence%20experience%2C%20including%20with%20Siri%20and%20Writing%20Tools.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20dissect%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%20more%20fully%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fiphone-16-review%23apple-intelligence%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiPhone%2016%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20in%20summary%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20distinguishing%20feature%20is%20Siri's%20integration%20with%20the%20ChatGPT%20AI%20chatbot%2C%20which%20essentially%20makes%20Siri%20much%20more%20useful%20and%20able%20to%20process%20significantly%20complex%20tasks.%20You%20can%20get%20help%20devising%20a%20workout%20plan%20or%20plan%20an%20entire%20trip%2C%20among%20many%20other%20things.%20It's%20like%20it%20does%20the%20research%20for%20you%2C%20or%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20it%20offers%20a%20good%20starting%20point%20for%20daunting%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20I%20like%20most%20about%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20AI%20chatbots%20is%20they%20give%20me%20a%20straight%20answer%20rather%20than%20offering%20a%20list%20of%20links%20to%20sift%20through%20myself%2C%20as%20previous%20AI%20assistants%20have.%20Just%20be%20aware%20that%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20AI%20chatbots%20can%20occasionally%20return%20with%20outdated%20and%20incorrect%20information%2C%20so%20it's%20best%20to%20double-check%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20answer%20seems%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iPhone%2016e%20on%20a%20wooden%20surface%20shown%20processing%20a%20prompt%20to%20create%20an%20AI-generated%20email%2C%20and%20another%20image%20showing%20the%20result.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c22a24b1834fe31165daed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWriting%20Tools%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20relieve%20you%20of%20ever%20writing%20an%20email%20again.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20headlining%20feature%20in%20Apple%20Intelligence%20is%20Writing%20Tools%2C%20which%20can%20be%20immensely%20useful.%20You%20can%20write%20entire%20emails%20with%20various%20tones%20based%20on%20short%20prompts%2C%20and%20it's%20excellent%20for%20summarizing%20longer%20emails.%20Shorthand%20notes%20in%20the%20Notes%20app%20can%20also%20be%20converted%20into%20full%20prose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iPhone%2016e%20held%20in%20a%20hand%20shown%20running%20Apple's%20Visual%20Intelligence%20feature%20providing%20advice%20on%20how%20to%20care%20for%20an%20orchid%20that%20it's%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c22abdb1834fe31165db18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVIsual%20Intelligence%20lets%20you%20point%20the%20camera%20to%20whatever%20sparks%20your%20curiosity%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20it.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVisual%20Intelligence%20lets%20you%20use%20your%20camera%20to%20identify%20and%20get%20more%20information%20on%20an%20object%2C%20like%20an%20unfamiliar%20plant.%20You%20can%20then%20ask%20more%20specific%20questions%2C%20like%20how%20to%20care%20for%20said%20plant.%20It%20works%20well%20and%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20your%20surroundings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Photos%20app%2C%20Apple%20Intelligence%20powers%20the%20Cleanup%20feature%2C%20which%20removes%20unwanted%20objects%20from%20a%20picture.%20It%20works%20well%20for%20smaller%20details%20but%20struggles%20to%20fill%20in%20the%20details%20behind%20larger%20objects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmaller%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%20include%20Genmoji%2C%20which%20lets%20you%20create%20an%20emoji%20of%20you