20Muzzle%20white%20running%20through%20a%20field.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5da73fcbcc4a0a6a212625c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20muzzles%20is%20the%20Bumas%20Muzzle%2C%20which%20is%20completely%20customizable%20for%20your%20dog.%3Cp%3EBumas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Bumas%20Muzzles%20are%20expensive%2C%20they%20are%20among%20the%20best%20dog%20muzzles%20on%20the%20market.%20Shikashio%20also%20recommends%20them.%20However%2C%20because%20the%20biothane%20material%20is%20not%20100%25%20bite-proof%2C%20he%20says%20they%20are%20best%20for%20dogs%20that%20are%20low-level%20biters%20rather%20than%20those%20with%20a%20more%20significant%20bite%20history.%20This%20custom-made%20muzzle%20cannot%20be%20returned%20or%20exchanged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22071c24f6-f353-4bf0-b07b-55c244f9f47e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20dog%20muzzle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20key%20elements%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20when%20shopping%20for%20one%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20muzzles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntended%20use%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instinctdogtraining.com%2Fpersonnel%2Fjennifer-malawey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJennifer%20Malawey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20certified%20professional%20dog%20trainer%20and%20behavioral%20consultant%20at%20Instinct%20Dog%20Behavior%20and%20Training%2C%20says%20there%20are%20several%20reasons%20why%20a%20dog%20might%20wear%20a%20muzzle.%20It's%20important%20to%20find%20the%20one%20that%20best%20suits%20your%20dog%20and%20the%20situation.%20For%20example%2C%20brief%20trips%20to%20the%20vet%20may%20only%20require%20a%20soft%20sleeve%20muzzle%20intended%20for%20short-term%20wear%2C%20while%20a%20basket%20muzzle%20might%20be%20best%20for%20longer%20walks.%20All%20muzzles%20used%20for%20extended%20wear%20must%20allow%20the%20dog%20to%20comfortably%20breathe%2C%20pant%2C%20drink%20water%2C%20and%20accept%20treats%2C%20Malawey%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFit%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20best%20dog%20muzzles%20will%20stay%20securely%20on%20your%20dog's%20head%2C%20Malawey%20says.%20Muzzles%20should%20have%20adjustable%20straps%20to%20loosen%20or%20tighten%20for%20a%20better%20fit.%20If%20you're%20opting%20for%20a%20muzzle%20without%20customization%20options%2C%20Malawey%20recommends%20moldable%20muzzles.%20They%20can%20help%20achieve%20a%20more%20secure%20fit%20in%20most%20dogs.%20Another%20aspect%20to%20consider%20is%20snout%20length.%20Large%20and%20small%20breeds%20will%20have%20different%20muzzle%20requirements%2C%20so%20avoid%20anything%20that's%20considered%20one%20size%20fits%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Durable%20materials%20like%20rubber%20and%20biothane%20are%20good%20options%20for%20the%20best%20dog%20muzzles.%20For%20sleeve%20muzzles%2C%20synthetic%20mesh%20typically%20works%20well%20to%20ensure%20airflow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExtra%20features%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Muzzles%20with%20extra%20safety%20straps%20may%20be%20useful%20in%20keeping%20a%20dog%20safe%2C%20but%20they%20are%20unnecessary.%20Options%20with%20fun%20colors%20or%20designs%20may%20also%20be%20a%20good%20choice%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20want%20to%20avoid%20some%20of%20the%20stigma%20of%20muzzling%20a%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bd9cdb02-246f-43eb-b276-b37461640b95%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20selected%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20selected%20the%20best%20dog%20muzzles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20made%20our%20choices%20for%20this%20guide%20based%20on%20recommendations%20and%20advice%20from%20Michael%20Shikashio%2C%20a%20certified%20animal%20behaviorist%20and%20dog%20aggression%20expert%3B%20Dr.%20Katherine%20Houpt%2C%20a%20veterinary%20behavi