ot%20fit%20all%20dogs%20perfectly.%20With%20only%20one%20adjustable%20strap%20and%20no%20way%20to%20shrink%20or%20expand%20the%20sleeve%2C%20it%20may%20not%20work%20for%20very%20small%20or%20large%20dogs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20short-snout%3A%20Trust%20Your%20Dog%20Muzzle%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20tan%20and%20white%20small%20breed%20wears%20a%20Trust%20Your%20Dog%20Custom%20rainbow%20Biothane%20Muzzle%20outside%20in%20a%20wooded%20area.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F610c137b38aff70018900b71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20muzzle%20is%20available%20in%20two%20designs%20that%20are%20ideal%20for%20short-snouted%20dogs.%3Cp%3ETrust%20Your%20Dog%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAvailable%20sizes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%206%20sizes%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterials%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Biothane%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EColors%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2028%20colors%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECustomization%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYes%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Custom%20fit%20for%20short-snouted%20dogs%2C%20two%20designs%20available%20for%20different%20security%20needs%2C%20straps%20come%20in%2028%20colors%20and%20can%20be%20mixed%20and%20matched%2C%20additional%20safety%20straps%20available%2C%20additional%20bling%20available%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Cannot%20be%20returned%2C%20takes%20up%20to%2012%20weeks%20to%20arrive%2C%20not%20100%25%20bite-proof%20for%20dogs%20with%20a%20bite%20history%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraditional%20basket%20and%20sleeve%20muzzles%20are%20designed%20to%20fit%20snugly%20around%20a%20dog's%20snout%2C%20but%20brachycephalic%20(short-snouted)%20pups%20like%20pugs%20and%20bulldogs%20need%20a%20different%20solution.%20For%20flat-faced%20dogs%2C%20Shikashio%20recommends%20handmade%20custom%20muzzles%20by%20Trust%20Your%20Dog.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20best%20dog%20muzzles%20for%20brachycephalic%20breeds%20and%20come%20in%20two%20designs%3A%20The%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftrust-your-dog.com%2Fproducts%2Fcustom-vinyl-muzzles%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Custom%20Vinyl%20Muzzle%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftrust-your-dog.com%2Fproducts%2Fcustom-biothane-muzzle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECustom%20Biothane%20Muzzle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20former%20looks%20more%20like%20a%20vinyl%20face%20shield%20than%20a%20standard%20basket%20design%20and%20features%20holes%20from%20top%20to%20bottom%20so%20a%20dog%20can%20easily%20drink%20water%20and%20eat%20treats.%20A%20colorful%20biothane%20strap%20wraps%20around%20the%20back%20of%20the%20head%20and%20is%20secured%20with%20quick-release%20metal%20or%20plastic%20buckles.%20Trust%20Your%20Dog%20recommends%20this%20style%20for%20dogs%20with%20a%20bite%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20design%2C%20the%20Custom%20Biothane%20Muzzle%2C%20has%20straps%20that%20wrap%20around%20the%20back%20of%20the%20head%20and%20over%20the%20forehead%20and%20secure%20with%20a%20quick-release%20metal%20or%20plastic%20buckle.%20You%20can%20also%20incorporate%20rhinestones%2C%20silver%20heart%20rivets%2C%20and%20brass%20stars%20into%20the%20design.%20The%20biothane%20muzzle%20may%20not%20be%20100%25%20effective%20at%20preventing%20dog%20bites%20in%20highly%20motivated%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biothane%20straps%20on%20the%20Custom%20Vinyl%20and%20Custom%20Biothane%20Muzzles%20can%20be%20mixed%20and%20matched%20from%2028%20colors%2C%20and%20additional%20safety%20straps%20are%20optional.%20Because%20Trust%20Your%20Dog%20Muzzles%20are%20handmade%20with%20a%20custom%20fit%2C%20they%20are%20more%20expensive%20than%20standard%20models%20and%20may%20take%20up%20to%2012%20weeks%20to%20