-with-a-turmeric-biz%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturmeric%3C%2Fa%3E%20cultivar%20created%20by%20Karekar.%20He%20was%20among%20a%20select%20group%20of%20grassroots%20innovators%20honoured%20by%20President%20Draupadi%20Murmu%20at%20the%2011th%20Biennial%20National%20Grassroots%20Innovation%20and%20Outstanding%20Traditional%20Knowledge%20Awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20local%20variety%20to%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20than%2030%20varieties%20grown%20in%20different%20states%2C%20SK4%20is%20the%20newest%20addition%20to%20the%20family%20of%20%3Cem%3ECurcuma%20Longa%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20the%20yellow%20spice%20we%20use%20in%20our%20food%2C%20ceremonies%2C%20and%20traditional%20Indian%20medicine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201152px)%20100vw%2C%201152px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FNewly-planted-saplings-in-a-row_11zon-1740633118.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Newly%20planted%20turmeric%20saplings%20deck%20field%20in%20Maharashtra%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FNewly-planted-saplings-in-a-row_11zon-1740633118.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FNewly-planted-saplings-in-a-row_11zon-1740633118-300x139.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FNewly-planted-saplings-in-a-row_11zon-1740633118-500x231.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FNewly-planted-saplings-in-a-row_11zon-1740633118-768x355.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FNewly-planted-saplings-in-a-row_11zon-1740633118-150x69.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-410057%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22532%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENewly%20planted%20turmeric%20saplings%20deck%20field%20in%20Maharashtra%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sangli%E2%80%99s%20Rajapuri%20Salem%20variety%20accounts%20for%2070%25%20of%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345836%2Fmadhya-pradesh-farmer-kanchan-verma-earns-double-income-growing-organic-turmeric%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturmeric%20production%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Though%20grown%20in%20over%2020%20states%2C%20the%20largest%20share%20is%20contributed%20by%20four%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F407624%2Fkrushi-sarathi-app-for-farmers-in-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMaharashtra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20In%202022-23%2C%20India%20produced%C2%A011.61%20lakh%20tonnes%C2%A0of%20turmeric%20making%20it%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20producer%2C%20consumer%2C%20and%20exporter.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%201998%2C%20I%20planted%20the%20local%20variety%2C%20Kadja%2C%20and%20observed%20a%20few%20plants%20that%20were%20early%20maturing%20and%20possessed%20good%20vigour.%20I%20harvested%20the%20produce%20from%20these%20plants%20and%20selected%20the%20ones%20untouched%20by%20disease%2C%20had%20bigger%20rhizomes%2C%20were%20bright%20in%20colour%20and%20high-yielding%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Karekar%2C%20who%20introduces%20himself%20as%20%E2%80%9C12%3Csup%3Eth%3C%2Fsup%3E%20fail%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20has%20been%20growing%20turmeric%20as%20an%20intercrop%20between%20the%20500%20areca%20nut%20palms%2C%20and%2050%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354850%2Fhomemaker-entrepreneur-organic-coconut-greenaura-oil-pickles-business-kerala-sumila-jayaraj%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoconut%20palms%3C%2Fa%3E%20standing%20on%20his%20family%20farm%20since%20the%20age%20of%2022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20call%20it%20SK-4%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202008%2C%20Karekar%20was%20able%20to%20develop%20a%20superior%20clone%20with%20all%20the%20desired%20traits%20and%20named%20it%20SK-4%2C%20taking%20the%20first%20letter%20of%20Shendge%20Kaka%2C%20the%20farmer%20who%20initially%20gave%20him%20tubers%20of%20Sangli%20Kadapa%20variety%2C%20Special%20Konkan%2C%20and%20his%20own%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202020%20Kharif%20season%2C%20the%20Dapoli-based%20Dr%20Balasaheb%20Sawant%20Konkan%20Krishi%20Vidyapeeth%20(DBSKKV)%20carried%20out%20validation%20trials%20at%20the%20National%20Innovation%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20(NIF)%20behest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnif.org.in%2Finnovation%2Fimproved-high-yielding-turmeric-variety%2F1143%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENIF%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20variety%20was%20promising%2C%20with%20a%20high%20rhizome%20yield%20(56t%2Fha).%20Among%20the%2032%20tested%20varieties%2C%20SK-4%20was%20observed%20to%20be%20superior%20over%2028%20check%20varieties%20and%20at%20par%20with%20the%20best%20check%20variety%20Sona%20(64t%2Fha)%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20yield%2Fha.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C