C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20disappointed%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20opportunities%20to%20discuss%20books%20with%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Heet.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20space%20where%20people%20could%20connect%2C%20share%20ideas%2C%20and%20form%20bonds%20over%20their%20love%20for%20books%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEstablishing%20Your%20Reading%20Circle%3A%20A%20space%20for%20readers%20in%20Ahmedabad%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20%E2%80%98Your%20Reading%20Circle%E2%80%99%20was%20born%20in%20September%202023%2C%20a%20space%20for%20avid%20readers%20in%20Ahmedabad%20to%20gather%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F344848%2Fnashik-bhimabai-jondhale-ajjichya-pustakancha-hotel-book-hotel-by-grandmother%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshare%20books%20and%20stories%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20conducted%20events%20in%20public%20places%20and%20created%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20for%20all%20interested%20readers%20to%20create%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20reading.%20As%20their%20community%20grew%2C%20another%20source%20of%20inspiration%20struck%20the%20duo%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20new%20idea%20they%20were%20eager%20to%20bring%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201915px)%20100vw%2C%201915px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FIMG_0331-1_11zon-1740461813.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221915%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20first%20mini%20public%20library%20was%20installed%20at%20Parimal%20Garden%2C%20Ahmedabad%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FIMG_03